               <msContents>
                  <summary>Prayer to Jesus Christ, “For the sake of Your Trinity,” በእንተ፡ ሥላሴከ።; Theological Treatise called Fruit of the Faith, ፍሬ፡ ሃይማኖት፡; Theological Treatise on the Incarnation of Jesus Christ, in Amharic and Gǝ‘ǝz; Beauty of Creation, ሥነ፡ ፍጥረት።; Five Pillars of Mystery, አምስቱ፡ አዕማደ፡ ምሥጢር፡; List of Heretics, አስማቲሆሙ፡ ለመናፍቃን፡; Commentary on the Daily Prayer, in Amharic, ትርጓሜ: ጸሎት: ዘዘወትር:; Commentary on Our Father, in Amharic, የአቡነ፡ ዘበሰማያት፡ ትርጓሜ፡; Hymn to the Trinity, “Praise to You,” ግናይ፡ ለክሙ።.</summary>
