                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4.3">
                     <locus from="21r" to="23r" facs="024">Fols 21r–23r</locus>
                     <title>For Monday</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">‎በዕለተ፡ ሠኑይ፡ በቀዳማይ፡ ሰዓተ፡ ሌሊት፡ ለይኵን፡ ጠፈር፡ ማዕከለ፡ ‎‎ሰማይ፡ ወምድር፡ ብሎ፡ ከዚህ፡ እስከ፡ ብሩህ፡ ሰማይ፡ የመላውን፡ ‎‎ወሀ፡ በሶስት፡ ከፍሎ፡ ለየው።‎ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4.4">
